        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> 1 minute (Interact)</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Astrolabes can be used for navigation in unfamiliar or featureless locations. To use an astrolabe, the holder must be trained in Survival.</p>\n<p>By spending 1 minute to measure the height of the stars and planets, a holder who knows the time and date can determine the latitude, and a holder who knows their latitude can determine the date and time.</p>\n<p>An astrolabe also grants a +1 item bonus on checks to identify celestial bodies. A mariner's astrolabe contains additional stabilizers that make it suitable for use on moving surfaces, such as the deck of a ship.</p>"
